"title": "1416: miracles, nature of",
"media_type": "Text",
"index_reference": "1416",
"language": "eng",
"review_level": "None",
"content": "<p>Miracles may be performed directly by God or through a human agent. Those recorded in Scripture include healing, raising the dead, miracles of nature and the casting out of demons.</p>\n<h2>Miracles demonstrate God's greatness and power</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps77:14\">PSA 77:14</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod14:30-Exod14:31\">EXO 14:30–14:31</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod34:10\">EXO 34:10</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut3:24\">DEU 3:24</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs18:37-1Kgs18:39\">1KI 18:37–18:39</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Job5:9\">JOB 5:9</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps78:4\">PSA 78:4</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke9:42-Luke9:43\">LUK 9:42–9:43</a></p>\n<h2>Miracles bringing God's judgment</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Lev10:1-Lev10:2\">LEV 10:1–10:2</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen19:24-Gen19:26\">GEN 19:24–19:26</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Num12:10\">NUM 12:10</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Num16:31-Num16:35\">NUM 16:31–16:35</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs13:4-1Kgs13:5\">1KI 13:4–13:5</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Kgs1:9-2Kgs1:12\">2KI 1:9–1:12</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Chr26:19-2Chr26:20\">2CH 26:19–26:20</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts5:5\">ACT 5:5</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts5:10\">ACT 5:10</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts13:11\">ACT 13:11</a></p>\n<h2>Miracles which meet human need</h2>\n<h3>The provision of food and water</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod17:6\">EXO 17:6</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod15:25\">EXO 15:25</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Num11:31-Num11:32\">NUM 11:31–11:32</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Num20:10-Num20:11\">NUM 20:10–20:11</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Judg15:18-Judg15:19\">JDG 15:18–15:19</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs17:5-1Kgs17:6\">1KI 17:5–17:6</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs17:8-1Kgs17:16\">1KI 17:8–17:16</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Kgs2:19-2Kgs2:22\">2KI 2:19–2:22</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Kgs4:42-2Kgs4:44\">2KI 4:42–4:44</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt14:15-Matt14:21\">MAT 14:15–14:21</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark8:1-Mark8:10\">MRK 8:1–8:10</a></p>\n<h3>Healing</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts5:16\">ACT 5:16</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Num21:6-Num21:9\">NUM 21:6–21:9</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Kgs5:1-2Kgs5:14\">2KI 5:1–5:14</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke9:6\">LUK 9:6</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts3:1-Acts3:10\">ACT 3:1–3:10</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts9:33-Acts9:34\">ACT 9:33–9:34</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts28:7-Acts28:9\">ACT 28:7–28:9</a></p>\n<h3>Exorcism</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts16:18\">ACT 16:18</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark6:13\">MRK 6:13</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark9:38\">MRK 9:38</a> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke9:49\">LUK 9:49</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke10:17\">LUK 10:17</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts8:7\">ACT 8:7</a></p>\n<h3>The raising of the dead</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/John11:38-John11:44\">JHN 11:38–11:44</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs17:17-1Kgs17:24\">1KI 17:17–17:24</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Kgs4:32-2Kgs4:37\">2KI 4:32–4:37</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Kgs13:21\">2KI 13:21</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts9:36-Acts9:41\">ACT 9:36–9:41</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts20:9-Acts20:12\">ACT 20:9–20:12</a></p>\n<h3>Miraculous births</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen18:10-Gen18:14\">GEN 18:10–18:14</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Judg13:2-Judg13:3\">JDG 13:2–13:3</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Sam1:20\">1SA 1:20</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Kgs4:14-2Kgs4:17\">2KI 4:14–4:17</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke1:34-Luke1:37\">LUK 1:34–1:37</a></p>\n<h3>Miracles involving military victory</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Chr32:21\">2CH 32:21</a></strong> parallels <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Kgs19:35-2Kgs19:36\">2KI 19:35–19:36</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa37:36-Isa37:37\">ISA 37:36–37:37</a> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod12:29-Exod12:36\">EXO 12:29–12:36</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod14:26-Exod14:28\">EXO 14:26–14:28</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Josh10:12-Josh10:14\">JOS 10:12–10:14</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Sam7:10-1Sam7:12\">1SA 7:10–7:12</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Kgs6:18-2Kgs6:23\">2KI 6:18–6:23</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Chr20:22-2Chr20:26\">2CH 20:22–20:26</a></p>\n<h3>Miraculous help in trouble</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Dan6:27\">DAN 6:27</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps91:11-Ps91:12\">PSA 91:11–91:12</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Dan3:19-Dan3:27\">DAN 3:19–3:27</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Dan6:19-Dan6:23\">DAN 6:19–6:23</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt8:23-Matt8:27\">MAT 8:23–8:27</a> parallels <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark4:36-Mark4:41\">MRK 4:36–4:41</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke8:22-Luke8:25\">LUK 8:22–8:25</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts12:6-Acts12:11\">ACT 12:6–12:11</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts16:25-Acts16:26\">ACT 16:25–16:26</a></p>\n<h3>Gifts of supernatural strength</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Judg14:5-Judg14:6\">JDG 14:5–14:6</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Judg14:19\">JDG 14:19</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Judg15:14-Judg15:16\">JDG 15:14–15:16</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Judg16:26-Judg16:30\">JDG 16:26–16:30</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs18:46\">1KI 18:46</a></p>\n<h3>Nature miracles</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Kgs2:7-2Kgs2:8\">2KI 2:7–2:8</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod10:13-Exod10:23\">EXO 10:13–10:23</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod14:15-Exod14:22\">EXO 14:15–14:22</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Josh3:14-Josh3:17\">JOS 3:14–3:17</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Kgs2:13-2Kgs2:14\">2KI 2:13–2:14</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt21:18-Matt21:22\">MAT 21:18–21:22</a> parallels <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark11:12-Mark11:14\">MRK 11:12–11:14</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark11:20-Mark11:24\">MRK 11:20–11:24</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John2:1-John2:11\">JHN 2:1–2:11</a></p>\n<h2>Miracles are part of God's plan of redemption</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Sam7:23\">2SA 7:23</a></strong> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Chr17:21\">1CH 17:21</a> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark16:17-Mark16:18\">MRK 16:17–16:18</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts2:22-Acts2:24\">ACT 2:22–2:24</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts14:3\">ACT 14:3</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Heb2:3-Heb2:4\">HEB 2:3–2:4</a></p>\n<h2>Miracles occur at times of special significance</h2>\n<h3>At the time of the exodus</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod3:2-Exod3:3\">EXO 3:2–3:3</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod7:3-Exod7:4\">EXO 7:3–7:4</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod16:11-Exod16:15\">EXO 16:11–16:15</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod17:6-Exod17:7\">EXO 17:6–17:7</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Num17:8\">NUM 17:8</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut4:34\">DEU 4:34</a></p>\n<h3>At times of national religious crisis</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs18:30-1Kgs18:39\">1KI 18:30–18:39</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Kgs3:16-2Kgs3:25\">2KI 3:16–3:25</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Kgs4:3-2Kgs4:7\">2KI 4:3–4:7</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Kgs4:40-2Kgs4:41\">2KI 4:40–4:41</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Kgs6:5-2Kgs6:7\">2KI 6:5–6:7</a></p>\n<h3>In the time of Jesus Christ</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt14:15-Matt14:21\">MAT 14:15–14:21</a> parallels <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark6:35-Mark6:44\">MRK 6:35–6:44</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke9:12-Luke9:17\">LUK 9:12–9:17</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John6:5-John6:13\">JHN 6:5–6:13</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt20:29-Matt20:34\">MAT 20:29–20:34</a> parallels <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark10:46-Mark10:52\">MRK 10:46–10:52</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke18:35-Luke18:43\">LUK 18:35–18:43</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John11:38-John11:44\">JHN 11:38–11:44</a></p>\n<h3>In the time of the first Christians</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke10:17\">LUK 10:17</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts8:6\">ACT 8:6</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts8:13\">ACT 8:13</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts14:8-Acts14:10\">ACT 14:8–14:10</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts14:19-Acts14:20\">ACT 14:19–14:20</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts19:11-Acts19:12\">ACT 19:11–19:12</a></p>\n<h2>Miracles are God's gift</h2>\n<h3>They authenticate the message of his servants</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/John10:38\">JHN 10:38</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod4:30-Exod4:31\">EXO 4:30–4:31</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt11:2-Matt11:5\">MAT 11:2–11:5</a> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke7:20-Luke7:22\">LUK 7:20–7:22</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark9:39\">MRK 9:39</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark16:20\">MRK 16:20</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John14:11\">JHN 14:11</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Cor12:12\">2CO 12:12</a></p>\n<h3>They are given by God's sovereign will</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Cor12:8-1Cor12:11\">1CO 12:8–12:11</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt10:1\">MAT 10:1</a> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke9:1\">LUK 9:1</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Cor12:28-1Cor12:30\">1CO 12:28–12:30</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gal3:5\">GAL 3:5</a></p>\n<h2>Miracles are not in themselves proof of God's work</h2>\n<h3>They are no guarantee of genuine faith</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt7:22-Matt7:23\">MAT 7:22–7:23</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke16:27-Luke16:31\">LUK 16:27–16:31</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John2:23-John2:24\">JHN 2:23–2:24</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Cor13:1-1Cor13:2\">1CO 13:1–13:2</a></p>\n<h3>They can be counterfeited</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt24:24\">MAT 24:24</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod7:11-Exod7:12\">EXO 7:11–7:12</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod7:22\">EXO 7:22</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod8:7\">EXO 8:7</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts8:9-Acts8:11\">ACT 8:9–8:11</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Thess2:9\">2TH 2:9</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev13:13\">REV 13:13</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev16:14\">REV 16:14</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev19:20\">REV 19:20</a></p>",
